Pattern Matching- Palindrome(A palindrome is as string that reads the same forwards and backwards).
race car: palindrome
"": palindrome

STRATEGY:01
left=0
right=n-1, the characters should be the same
len= even, len=odd

STRATEGY:02(reverse of solution01)
left,right=centre

STRATEGY:03
Transform into the one without the spaces.
Create a duplicate of the string in reverse/flip.
